  "@type": "ActorManifest",
  "id": "did:web:etzhayyim.com:funadaiku",
  "name": "funadaiku",
  "displayName": "船大工 — Zero-Emission Autonomous Cargo Shipbuilding",
  "displayNameJa": "船大工 (ふなだいく)",
  "displayNameEn": "Funadaiku",
  "description": "Zero-emission autonomous cargo-ship building Tier-B actor. Surface counterpart of watatsumi (綿津見 submersible); reuses watatsumi's modular grand-block shipyard methodology and the kami-autodrive ShipHydro GNC. Defining subsystem: a wind-assist + solar + hydrogen fuel-cell + LFP-battery + electric-pod powertrain with NO fossil main or auxiliary engine (G13). Naval / armed / nuclear / fossil-propulsion vessels are constitutional non-goals per Charter Rider §2(a)+§2(d).",
  "descriptionJa": "ゼロエミッション自律貨物船の設計・建造を司る Tier-B actor。綿津見 (潜水艇) の水上対応版。綿津見のモジュラー・グランドブロック工法と kami-autodrive ShipHydro GNC を再利用し、風力補助 + 太陽光 + 水素燃料電池 + LFP バッテリ + 電動ポッド推進(化石主機・補機ゼロ, G13)を定義サブシステムとする。海軍・武装・原子力・化石燃料推進船は Charter Rider §2(a)+§2(d) の constitutional non-goal。",
  "adr": {
    "master": "etzhayyim:adr:2606013400",
    "r0": "etzhayyim:adr:2606013400",
    "r1": "etzhayyim:adr:2606013415",
    "r2": "etzhayyim:adr:2606013430",
    "r3": "etzhayyim:adr:2606013445"
  },
  "tier": "Tier-B",
  "siblings": [
    "did:web:etzhayyim.com:watatsumi",
